Perl script to download daily newspaper De Standaard and the extras

Needed from CPAN:
WWW::Mechanize
HTML::Form
CAM::PDF
Getopt::Std

Currently supported command-line options are:
-D: Get the whole daily newspaper
-v: Get the part Vooraan in de krant
-b: Get the part Binnenland en buitenland
-o: Get the part Opinie & Analyse
-s: Get the part Sport
-e: Get the part Economie
-u: Get the part Beurs

Examples:
Get everything:
./getstandaard -D
Get only Vooraan in de krant
./getstandaard -Dv
Get Sport and Economie
./getstandaard -Dse
Get DS Weekblad
./getstandaard -W
Get DSM
./getstandaard -S
Get Reizen
./getstandaard -R
Get Letteren
./getstandaard -L

